text: Dieter Gröning (born 26 July 1932) is an Australian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle flyweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Australia Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gdańsk
